l-replaced-content' style='box-sizing: inherit; display: block; height: 0px; max-height: 100%; max-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; min-width: 100%; width: 0px; margin: auto; padding: 0px !important; border: none !important; position: absolute; inset: 0px; object-fit: contain;'>\n    </amp-img>\n</p>\n<p data-amp-original-style='text-align: center;' class='amp-wp-cdd8ca0' style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><em style='box-sizing: inherit;'>Túi gia vị thảo mộc rất quan trọng trong quy trình nấu phở</em></p>\n<h3 style='box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(244, 116, 33); margin: 0px 0px 5px; text-transform: capitalize; clear: both; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span id='Cach_nau_nuoc_dung_pho_bo' style='box-sizing: inherit;'>Cách Nấu Nước Dùng Phở Bò</span></h3>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>Xương ống bò rửa sạch. Bắc nồi nước lên bếp cùng với một ít sả cây đun sôi. Cho xương vào chần sơ qua để khử đi mùi hôi.</p>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>\n    <amp-img class='aligncenter size-full wp-image-41459 amp-wp-enforced-sizes i-amphtml-layout-intrinsic i-amphtml-layout-size-defined i-amphtml-element i-amphtml-built i-amphtml-layout' src='https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/chan-xuong-bo.jpg' alt='chần xương bò' width='620' height='400' srcset='https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/chan-xuong-bo.jpg 620w, https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/chan-xuong-bo-400x258.jpg 400w, https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/chan-xuong-bo-300x194.jpg 300w' layout='intrinsic' i-amphtml-layout='intrinsic' i-amphtml-auto-lightbox-visited='' lightbox='i-amphtml-auto-lightbox-3' on='tap:amp-lightbox-gallery.activate' style='box-sizing: inherit; border-style: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; height: auto; max-width: 100%; d