ss: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><em style='box-sizing: inherit;'>Chần xương bò qua nước sôi để làm sạch</em></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>Vớt xương đã chần ra, cho vào khay cùng với gừng, hành tím, hành tây cắt múi cau đem đi nướng đến khi xương vàng, lấy xương ra khỏi lò, cho ngay vào thau nước đá.</p>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>\n    <amp-img class='aligncenter size-full wp-image-41460 amp-wp-enforced-sizes i-amphtml-layout-intrinsic i-amphtml-layout-size-defined i-amphtml-element i-amphtml-built i-amphtml-layout' src='https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nuong-xuong.jpg' alt='nướng xương' width='620' height='400' srcset='https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nuong-xuong.jpg 620w, https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nuong-xuong-400x258.jpg 400w, https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nuong-xuong-300x194.jpg 300w' layout='intrinsic' i-amphtml-layout='intrinsic' i-amphtml-auto-lightbox-visited='' lightbox='i-amphtml-auto-lightbox-4' on='tap:amp-lightbox-gallery.activate' style='box-sizing: inherit; border-style: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; height: auto; max-width: 100%; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden !important; clear: both; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;'>\n        <i-amphtml-sizer class='i-amphtml-sizer' slot='i-amphtml-svc' style='box-sizing: inherit; display: block !important; max-width: 100%;'><img alt='' aria-hidden='true' class='i-amphtml-intrinsic-sizer' role='presentation' src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,<svg height=&quot;400&quot; width=&quot;620&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot;/>' i-amphtml-auto-lightbox-visited='' style='box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; display: block !important;'></i-amphtml-sizer><img decoding='async' sizes='(max-width: 1536px) 835px, 100vw' alt='nướng xương' srcset='https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nuong-xuong.jpg 620w, https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nuong-xuong-400x258.jpg 400w, https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nuong-xuong-300x194.jpg 300w' src='https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nuong-xuong.jpg' class='i-amphtml-fill-content i-amphtml-replaced-content' style='box-sizing: inherit; display: block; height: 0px; max-height: 100%; max-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; min-width: 100%; width: 0px; margin: auto; padding: 0px !important; border: none !important; position: absolute; inset: 0px; object-fit: contain;'>\n    </amp-img>\n</p>\n<p data-amp-original-style='text-align: center;' class='amp-wp-cdd8ca0' style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><em style='box-sizing: inherit;'>Nướng xương là cách để nước dùng thơm, đậm vị hơn</em></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>Đun sôi một nồi nước, cho xương bò đã nướng, gói gia vị vừa làm, hành tây, gừng đã nướng, sả vào nồi nước. Hầm xương khoảng 5 – 6 tiếng cho ra nước ngọt. Trong lúc hầm xương, bạn cho thịt bắp bò vào luộc chín. Lưu ý là luộc thịt bắp bò chín thì vớt ra ngay nếu để quá lâu thịt sẽ bị mềm nhũn. Sau đó vớt các nguyên liệu ra, lọc lấy nước dùng.</p>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>Bắc nồi nước dùng đã lọc lên bếp, nêm một ít muối, bột ngọt, hạt nêm, đường phèn sao cho vừa ăn, đun sôi và tắt bếp.</p>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>\n    <amp-img class='aligncenter size-full wp-image-41461 amp-wp-enforced-sizes i-amphtml-layout-intrinsic i-amphtml-layout-size-defined i-amphtml-element i-amphtml-built i-amphtml-layout' src='https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nem-nem-gia-vi-cho-nuoc-dung.jpg' alt='nêm nếm gia vị cho nước dùng' width='620' height='400' srcset='https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nem-nem-gia-vi-cho-nuoc-dung.jpg 620w, https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nem-nem-gia-vi-cho-nuoc-dung-400x258.jpg 400w, https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nem-nem-gia-vi-cho-nuoc-dung-300x194.jpg 300w' layout='intrinsic' i-amphtml-layout='intrinsic' i-amphtml-auto-lightbox-visited='' lightbox='i-amphtml-auto-lightbox-5' on='tap:amp-lightbox-gallery.activate' style='box-sizing: inherit; border-style: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; height: auto; max-width: 100%; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden !important; clear: both; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;'>\n        <i-amphtml-sizer class='i-amphtml-sizer' slot='i-amphtml-svc' style='box-sizing: inherit; display: block !important; max-width: 100%;'><img alt='' aria-hidden='true' class='i-amphtml-intrinsic-sizer' role='presentation' src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,<svg height=&quot;400&quot; width=&quot;620&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot;/>' i-amphtml-auto-lightbox-visited='' style='box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; display: block !important;'></i-amphtml-sizer><img decoding='async' sizes='(max-width: 1536px) 835px, 100vw' alt='nêm nếm gia vị cho nước dùng' srcset='https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nem-nem-gia-vi-cho-nuoc-dung.jpg 620w, https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nem-nem-gia-vi-cho-nuoc-dung-400x258.jpg 400w, https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nem-nem-gia-vi-cho-nuoc-dung-300x194.jpg 300w' src='https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/nem-nem-gia-vi-cho-nuoc-dung.jpg' class='i-amphtml-fill-content i-amphtml-replaced-content' style='box-sizing: inherit; display: block; height: 0px; max-height: 100%; max-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; min-width: 100%; width: 0px; margin: auto; padding: 0px !important; border: none !important; position: absolute; inset: 0px; object-fit: contain;'>\n    </amp-img>\n</p>\n<p data-amp-original-style='text-align: center;' class='amp-wp-cdd8ca0' style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><em style='box-sizing: inherit;'>Nêm nếm gia vị cho nước dùng</em></p>\n<h3 style='box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(244, 116, 33); margin: 0px 0px 5px; text-transform: capitalize; clear: both; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span id='Trinh_bay_va_thuong_thuc' style='box-sizing: inherit;'>Trình Bày Và Thưởng Thức</span></h3>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>Thịt bò phi lê rửa sạch, thái lát mỏng.</p>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>Thịt bò bắp thái lát mỏng.</p>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>Chần giá và đầu hành qua nước sôi.</p>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>Chần bánh phở qua nước sôi.</p>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>Cho giá, đầu hành, bánh phở vào tô, xếp thịt bắp bò, thịt phi lê, hành lá, ngò rí, hành tây, ớt cắt lát rồi chan nước dùng vào.</p>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>Bạn thưởng thức phở cùng với các loại rau ăn kèm, tương ớt, tương đen.</p>\n<p style='box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>\n    <amp-img class='aligncenter size-full wp-image-41462 amp-wp-enforced-sizes i-amphtml-layout-intrinsic i-amphtml-layout-size-defined i-amphtml-element i-amphtml-built i-amphtml-layout' src='https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/chan-nuoc-dung.jpg' alt='chan nước dùng' width='620' height='400' srcset='https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/chan-nuoc-dung.jpg 620w, https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/chan-nuoc-dung-400x258.jpg 400w, https://cdn.huongnghiepaau.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/chan-nuoc-dung-300x194.jpg 300w' layout='intrinsic' i-amphtml-layout='intrinsic' i-amphtml-auto-lightbox-visited='' lightbox='i-amphtml-auto-l